name: Joker Stencil
description: Multi Layered stencil of Heath Ledger as The Joker. Created using spray paint and acrylic paint. 16" x 12" canvas board. Signed and dated.

name: Canary Watercolour Painting
description:
Watercolour painting of a Canary. Created by Becky Watson. Done on A3 cartridge paper. 

Becky Watson is a fantastic artist and in her first year at art college, she got entered in to the Lloyds TSB Art Of Nurture competition where she reached the Regional finals. 

I'll be selling more of Becky's work for her so keep checking back for more!
